{"tid":847015,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天氣轉涼 打鼓嶺周六或低見19℃","createTime":"2018-10-04T00:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T01:35:35.000Z","uid":36868,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"16a4bfad42e70b6d636bcc295525e8418fb615df","tid":847015,"uid":36868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T00:38:40.000Z","msg":"【晴報專訊】踏入10月秋意更濃，小心日夜溫差大！根據天文台自動分區天氣預報顯示，周末起新界多區氣溫差異極大，其中打鼓嶺最低只得19度，與日間最高的31度相差達12度；而上水、石崗等地最低亦只有20度，顯示天氣愈見清涼。<br />\n<br />\n天文台科學主任羅曉輝表示，受東北季候風影響，為華南地區帶來晴朗及非常乾燥的天氣，晴朗天氣導致輻射冷卻加速，令本港日夜溫差頗大，當中遠離海邊及較空曠的新界地區，更會再低1、2度，市民應注意保暖。天文台又預測，一股偏東氣流會在下周初影響廣東沿岸，屆時本港雲量會增多，並有幾陣雨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%A3%E8%BD%89%E6%B6%BC-%E6%89%93%E9%BC%93%E5%B6%BA%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AD%E6%88%96%E4%BD%8E%E8%A6%8B19-224548520.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E8%25BD%2589%25E6%25B6%25BC-%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%25BC%2593%25E5%25B6%25BA%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2588%2596%25E4%25BD%258E%25E8%25A6%258B19-224548520.html&d=H3DcRIHP3HVBLs8OlYA0urr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=0febf03f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%A3%E8%BD%89%E6%B6%BC-%E6%89%93%E9%BC%93%E5%B6%BA%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AD%E6%88%96%E4%BD%8E%E8%A6%8B19-224548520.html</a>"},{"pid":"0bfb586600281703340527343a289c1463527019","tid":847015,"uid":36868,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T00:39:16.000Z","msg":"好興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快D到冬天"},{"pid":"2b05da6b8fdf817c9d259699e49342368f263cbf","tid":847015,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T00:44:42.000Z","msg":"睇埋北潭涌先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75417b3853dc4c4ea05510ed91ad525d7ebfceed","tid":847015,"uid":922,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T00:50:23.000Z","msg":"最近天氣開始轉涼了<img src=\"/assets/faces/no